hexadecimal color
FF is max 00 is lowest

color: rgb(255,255,255)
color: rgba(0,0,0,.5) - a is the opacity btw 0-1

color pickers - MAC DigitalColor Meter
shift cmd c will copy text color, can paste in sublime ie. 97  66  38  





